children.text: How many cigarettes did you used to smoke daily?
How many cigarettes does your usual cigarette box have?
What was the price of your usual cigarette box?

Welcome to Drop It!


We're happy to know that you took the hard decision of stop smoking. Congratulations!

Drop It! plans to help you every day, trying to motivate you to do it and remembering why you chosen this way.

To start, we need to know something about you.We have to ask you some questions.If you're not sure about it, no problem! You can edit them in the future.
